title: Ecocafe
typeOfFood: Organic, Juice bar, Bakery, European, Hungarian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Bio coffee shop and bakery on Andrassy ut with a nice atmosphere and free Wi-Fi. There are sandwiches, salads, fresh juices, and coffee drinks (has soymilk). Beware that some desserts are labeled as vegan even though honey is used - ask.
